### 11.2 Detected Gaps & Mitigations

| # | Gap | Impact | Mitigation |
|---|-----|--------|------------|
| 1 | **No refresh_token in backend** | Session expires after 12h, forces re-login | Set longer cookie expiry; implement server-side session cache; **FIX BACKEND** |
| 2 | **Backend auth creates its own DB session** | May bypass RLS setup in `get_db()` | Verify auth endpoints work with tenant context; test thoroughly |
| 3 | **Payment list N+1 query** | Performance issue at scale | Frontend pagination + virtualization; backend fix recommended |
| 4 | **No rate limiting** | DOS risk | Add Cloudflare rate limiting or nginx `limit_req` |
| 5 | **AuditLog incomplete** | Payments/ledger lack audit entries | Frontend console logging; push for backend fix |
| 6 | **Sequence race condition** | Duplicate sale numbers under load | DB constraint catches it; retry logic in frontend |
| 7 | **No frontend code exists** | System is unusable | **THIS SPEC IS THE BLUEPRINT** |

### 11.3 Financial Safety Guarantees

- ✅ **All money is integer** — No floating-point arithmetic in frontend
- ✅ **Currency formatting** — `formatCurrency()` handles all display
- ✅ **Installment math** — Client-side preview matches backend exactly
- ✅ **FIFO allocation** — Visual preview matches backend allocation logic
- ✅ **Ledger display** — Read-only, derived from backend, no client-side ledger mutation
- ✅ **Idempotency** — All POST operations include `idempotency_key`

### 11.4 Auth Safety Guarantees

- ✅ **HTTP-Only cookies** — No JWT in localStorage (XSS protection)
- ✅ **SameSite=lax** — Cloudflare-compatible cookie policy
- ✅ **Path=/** — Cookie accessible on all routes
- ✅ **Middleware validation** — Every route protected, RBAC enforced
- ✅ **Token expiry handling** — 401 redirects to login
- ✅ **No refresh token workaround documented** — Fallback strategy defined

